pr_title: feat(core+login): add Core Module and Login component
pr_body:
# Modules Introduced
## Core Module
- Core Module is repsonsible for handling authentication , authorization and logging and redering all the pages.
- Shell Component inside the Core Module makes use of the Authentication guard to render the pages as per the authorizations.
## Shared Module
- Shared Module exports the material components and icons


# Functionalities Introduced
- Authentication using the Fineract self-service endpoints

- [ x ] All files pass linting  
- Video Screencast
